{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-033__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-033", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-033__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "chapter", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 33", "sort_key": "033.000", "text_original": "知人者智，自知者明。\n\n勝人者有力，自勝者強。\n\n知足者富。\n\n強行者有志。\n\n不失其所者久。\n\n死而不亡者壽。", "text_normalized": "知人者智，自知者明。\n\n勝人者有力，自勝者強。\n\n知足者富。\n\n強行者有志。\n\n不失其所者久。\n\n死而不亡者壽。", "notes": ""}
